{"id": "1192625362690117692", "channel_id": "1192459744355565690", "type": 0, "author_id": "512229576416559117", "author_name": "vancelu", "author_bot": false, "content": "Pve而已強度超模又如何 是關卡不敢讓玩家過？以後出新角幻夢能打7000以上就等著被砍", "timestamp": "2024-01-05T00:27:24.373000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1192459744355565690", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【V1.0.29】在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1192630911775293450", "channel_id": "1192459744355565690", "type": 0, "author_id": "950676449050894377", "author_name": "xxxxx7446", "author_bot": false, "content": "我只感受到官方的傲慢，把自己的问题平摊给所有玩家头上，让玩家的真金白银给官方“付费测试”。\n我只能说真改了大家该卸载卸载，该1星1星，我们是玩家，不是傻逼。", "timestamp": "2024-01-05T00:49:27.378000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1192459744355565690", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【V1.0.29】在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1192630960315957338", "channel_id": "1192459744355565690", "type": 0, "author_id": "855841735150141452", "author_name": "th00000000_", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且砍的還是限定角 限定角資源不夠要課金抽 強度比較強也不為過吧 加上前期要累積斷頭傷害也不是關卡都無腦過啊 圖魯已經被砍了 夫人再被砍 下次新的限定角沒人敢抽了", "timestamp": "2024-01-05T00:49:38.951000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1192459744355565690", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【V1.0.29】在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1192631312633319574", "channel_id": "1192459744355565690", "type": 19, "author_id": "855841735150141452", "author_name": "th00000000_", "author_bot": false, "content": "看來我是頭號鐵傻🥺", "timestamp": "2024-01-05T00:51:02.950000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["950676449050894377"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1192630911775293450", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1192459744355565690", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【V1.0.29】在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1192631372771237928", "channel_id": "1192459744355565690", "type": 0, "author_id": "950676449050894377", "author_name": "xxxxx7446", "author_bot": false, "content": "这好像是在说：我买了一件商品后刚用不久，官方就冲进我家说这件商品太好用影响我之后的售卖然后把我都已经买到手的商品拆了？\n\n滑天下之大稽。", "timestamp": "2024-01-05T00:51:17.288000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1192459744355565690", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【V1.0.29】在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1192632444877283512", "channel_id": "1192459744355565690", "type": 0, "author_id": "1192423798310453419", "author_name": "xikecuige", "author_bot": false, "content": "限定up还没结束就开始出砍的公告，是数值策划脑子有问题还是觉得玩家都是atm只要给钱就完事了", "timestamp": "2024-01-05T00:55:32.898000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1192459744355565690", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【V1.0.29】在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1192633595437785241", "channel_id": "1192459744355565690", "type": 0, "author_id": "950676449050894377", "author_name": "xxxxx7446", "author_bot": false, "content": "我只能说官方非常希望像提线木偶一样把玩家的强度掌握在手里，甚至还出了“不应该打得过”的70级，就为了让我们进去瞅一眼然后被官方刻意安排的难度打翻在地。\n\n然后被玩家打过了急眼了，急吼吼要削之前测试了两次都没测出来的限定角色。\n\n我觉得这不是急性脑梗死能解释的，更大概率是小脑发育不完全大脑完全不发育才有的想法。", "timestamp": "2024-01-05T01:00:07.213000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-05T01:01:55.623000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1192459744355565690", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【V1.0.29】在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1192635203198402591", "channel_id": "1192459744355565690", "type": 0, "author_id": "855841735150141452", "author_name": "th00000000_", "author_bot": false, "content": "單點高爆傷害是夫人的優點也是缺點 在關卡中適當加入怪物屏障或是招喚小怪的能力 其實就可以有效抑制隊伍單一化的問題", "timestamp": "2024-01-05T01:06:30.533000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1192459744355565690", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【V1.0.29】在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1192722395732127815", "channel_id": "1192459744355565690", "type": 0, "author_id": "428521987934257164", "author_name": "chuchiyung", "author_bot": false, "content": "樓上的發言真的。。不要人身攻擊喔\n然後 官方不是說會補償自選嗎 包括原型視界之類的", "timestamp": "2024-01-05T06:52:58.853000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1192459744355565690", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【V1.0.29】在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
